			Stephen Colbert (now sans &quot;Colbeard&quot;) has named Jon Batiste as the new bandleader for his new &quot;Late Show.&quot;<br />
<br />
Batiste, who is from New Orleans and studied at Juilliard, hails from a long line of celebrated musicians in Louisiana and grew up playing percussion and then piano in his family's band. He also appeared as himself on the HBO series &quot;Treme.&quot;<br />
